dct_title_s: The State of New Jersey, compiled from the most authentic information
dct_description_sm: Prime meridian: Philadelphia. Relief shown pictorially. Shows towns, county boundaries, and the "Division line of East and West Jersey." "Engraved for Carey's American edition of Guthrie's Geography improved."
dct_subject_sm: New Jersey—Administrative and political divisions—Maps—Early works to 1800
dcat_theme_sm: New Jersey—Administrative and political divisions—Maps—Early works to 1800
